public interface PieDataset<K extends Comparable<K>> extends KeyedValues<K>, Dataset
A general purpose dataset where values are associated with keys. As the name suggests, you can use this dataset to supply data for pie charts (refer to the org.jfree.chart.plot.PiePlot class).
